            "settings": {
              "tabs": [
                {
                  "_id": "fq1",
                  "tab_title": "Is there a minimum commitment?",
                  "tab_content": "<p>Yes. Real results take time. Foundations is a 3-month minimum, Flagship runs 6 months, Apex is ongoing retainer.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "_id": "fq2",
                  "tab_title": "Do you take remote / online clients?",
                  "tab_content": "<p>Only in Tier 02 (Flagship) and Tier 03 (Apex). Foundations requires in-person sessions at the Ft. Lauderdale studio for the full 90 days.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "_id": "fq3",
                  "tab_title": "I have a history of injuries. Am I a fit?",
                  "tab_content": "<p>Almost certainly yes. A huge part of the work is rebuilding movement and pain-free strength. Flag injuries in the brief so we can scope the assessment properly.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "_id": "fq4",
                  "tab_title": "Who shouldn't apply?",
                  "tab_content": "<p>Anyone looking for a templated plan, group fitness, or a guarantee without work. The method only works if you show up and execute.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "_id": "fq5",
                  "tab_title": "What happens after I submit?",
                  "tab_content": "<p>Billy's team reads every brief personally. If the fit looks right, we schedule a 45-minute consultation within 48 hours. If not, you'll hear back with honest guidance.</p>"
                }
              ],
              "title_html_tag": "div",
